comments: Mobley (CLE) moves alongside Randle's (NYK) path and he absorbs the marginal contact at the end of the drive.
Osman (CLE) briefly rests his arm on Randle's (NYK) side and marginal contact occurs at the end of the drive.
Osman (CLE) legally contests Hart's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Garland (CLE) is already in Randle's (NYK) path and is firming up as he absorbs the contact.
Mobley (CLE) is already in Grimes' (NYK) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Grimes (NYK) legally contests Mitchell's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Randle (NYK) legally contests Mitchell's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Mitchell (CLE) moves forward into Hart (NYK) and dislodges him as Hart secures possession.
Garland (CLE) and Randle (NYK) come together at the same spot and the contact off-ball is marginal.
Grimes (NYK) firms up in Osman's (CLE) path and he absorbs the contact to his upper body.
Garland (CLE) steps slightly forward towards Brunson's (NYK) path and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Osman (CLE) legally contests Brunson's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Grimes (NYK) brings his forearm towards Mitchell's (CLE) front and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Grimes (NYK) does not maintain legal guarding position and makes contact with Mitchell's (CLE) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Grimes (NYK) is already in Osman's (CLE) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Osman (CLE) brushes Brunson's (NYK) arm and the contact is marginal.
Mitchell (CLE) legally contests Hart's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Hartenstein (NYK) and Allen (CLE) briefly engage and disengage as marginal contact occurs while they pursue the rebound.
Osman (CLE) brushes Brunson's (NYK) front after the release of his driving shot attempt, and the contact is marginal.
Grimes (NYK) places his hand momentarily on Mitchell's (CLE) side and the contact is marginal.
Randle (NYK) moves towards Allen (CLE) and marginal contact occurs during the shot near the rim.
Osman (CLE) legally contests Brunson's (NYK) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Randle (NYK) pursues the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Mobley (CLE) as he moves towards the rim.
Garland (CLE) commits a take foul on Grimes (NYK). The game clock continues to run after the whistle to 4.3, and it should have been reset to 5.3.
Grimes (NYK) is retreating alongside Mitchell's (CLE) path as he contests the jump shot attempt.
